Package: tinylens
Title: Tidy Image Analysis for Digital Humanities
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Nabeel Siddiqui [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Nabeel Siddiqui <nabeel@example.com>
Description: A tidy, pipeable toolkit for image-first analysis targeting digital 
    humanities and film studies. Provides functions for loading image collections,
    extracting color metrics, texture features, composition analysis, face/object
    detection, and neural embeddings. All functions return tidy tibbles with one 
    row per image and scalar feature columns for easy downstream analysis.
